          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-02-14 22:43:03" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>that which constitutes an unwanted spot or stain upon something</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>spot</Gloss>
                <Gloss>stain</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible that in {S:06500101200016} σπιλάς means an ‘unseen danger,’ in that it may refer to a rock which is mostly or completely covered by the sea (see {D:21.5}).</Comments>
